name: Fear of the Dark #02 - Dark - Diptych
description:
DARK is the second part of the diptych exploring the theme of "Fear of the dark" (as the eponym song), viewer discretion is advised when alone in the dark.

“Thou shalt not be afraid for the terror by night, 
Nor for the arrow that flieth by day.”
Psalms 91:5

Vectorized handstyle.
PIXEL 7016x4960 (Retina resolution)
DPI 300 
9,21Mo
